## Deploy Decision Tree

```
What changed?
├── New migrations?        → Step 2 of deploy.py shows pending list → confirm with Raf → Step 6 runs them
├── New .env keys?         → SFTP .env update BEFORE triggering cPanel deploy
├── composer.json changed? → Rebuild vendor/ locally first, commit, then deploy
├── Blade layouts changed? → Step 5c checks for @vite and @livewireScripts regressions
└── PayrollParseService?   → Must test all 3 AM Excel formats after deploy
```

