## Known Issues — Quick Reference

Full details in `references/known-issues.md`. Critical ones:

| # | Issue | Trigger | Fix |
|---|---|---|---|
| 1 | Apache 404 | DNS mismatch | Update `hr` A record in Bluehost Zone Editor |
| 2 | PHP 500 | Wrong handler | `.htaccess` must have `___lsphp` (already correct — don't change) |
| 3 | App crashes post-deploy | `.env` wiped by `cp -R` | `head -4 .env` → verify `APP_ENV=production` |
| 4 | Vite 500 | `@vite()` in layouts | Remove `@vite` — no Node.js on Bluehost |
| 5 | Blank / broken Livewire UI | Dual Alpine | Use **`@livewireScripts`** only; **do not** also load Alpine.js from a CDN in the same layout (loads Alpine twice). Older docs mentioned `@livewireScriptConfig` + separate Alpine — current app loads Livewire’s bundle only. |
| 6 | `migrate` fails fresh | Timestamp order bug | `->after('hours')` before `hours` column exists — fixed in `f2f0de0` |
| 7 | Zero payroll entries | Parser format mismatch | Test all 3 AM Excel files after any PayrollParseService change |
| 8 | Ancient dates in payroll | Bad serial date parse | `DELETE FROM payroll_records WHERE YEAR(check_date) < 2015 AND user_id = 7` |
| 9 | Uploads 404 | Missing storage symlink | `php artisan storage:link` |
| 10 | Wrong margin numbers | `am_earnings` corruption | Re-upload all 3 AM Excel files + Recompute Margins |

